Package: stAirPol
Type: Package
Title: Spatio-temporal Modelling of Air Pollution Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Maxi Kellerbauer
Maintainer: Maxi Kellerbauer <maxi.kellerbauer@googlemail.com>
Description: Spatio-temporal Modelling of Air Pollution Data. This package takes the air pollution data from www.luftdaten.info, combines that data with metrological data from the Deutschen Wetter Dienst and aggregates it to different time intervals. With that aggregated data it's possible to perform Bayesian hierarchical spatio temporal modelling on it. The Bayesian Modelling is based on the spTimer package.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: DBI, RSQLite, curl, data.table, ggplot2, pbmcapply, sf, spTimer, MASS, Rcpp, automap, dplyr, dplyr, ggsn, lubridate, parallel, pbmcapply, readr, sf, sp
